OL,3,CTeen calls for more bereavement
OL,4,Csupport after father's sudden death
OL,6,FHis 15-year-old daughter, Holly, was
OL,7,Fthere for his final moments, and now
OL,8,Fshe's calling for more support for
OL,9,Fothers like her.
OL,11,F"He was an amazing dad. He was really
OL,12,Floving, really kind, very adventurous.
OL,13,FI was holding his hand and stuff. So
OL,14,Fthat was last time I saw him."
OL,16,FFollowing his death, she was supported
OL,17,Fby the Harrogate charity, Just B.
OL,19,FHolly said it helped her deal with her
OL,20,Fgrief and the traumatic circumstances
OL,21,Fin which her father died.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
