OL,3,CTeen calls for more bereavement
OL,4,Csupport after father's sudden death
OL,6,F"Just talking to Emma really helped
OL,7,Ftalk about my emotions. And then
OL,8,Fslowly, just starting to talk about it
OL,9,Fmore and more.
OL,11,F"And then I just found coping
OL,12,Fmechanisms for me. Over time it's
OL,13,Fgotten better."
OL,15,FHowever, the charity said it is facing
OL,16,Fa growing demand for help.
OL,18,FIt says its services are almost now at
OL,19,Fcrisis point, putting even more
OL,20,Fpressure on finances.
