OL,3,CTeen calls for more bereavement
OL,4,Csupport after father's sudden death
OL,6,FIt already costs around #1m a year to
OL,7,Foperate.
OL,9,FEmma, Holly's support worker from the
OL,10,Forganisation, said:
OL,12,F"There are quite a lot of people who
OL,13,Fwalk through the door and assume that
OL,14,Fmaybe we are NHS or a shame that were
OL,15,Ffunded through some form of government
OL,16,Fbody, but we're not.
OL,18,F"We are a charity, who are growing and
OL,19,Fdeveloping as the demand grows. But
OL,20,Fwith that, we need the income."
